{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/sge_discord_banner.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/sandy_horizontal_runner_small.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>Sandy's Great Escape is a charming, pixel art puzzle game with nostalgic box pushing mechanics and a forgiving rewind mechanic. Death is never the end for Sandy, as you magically respawn and use your shell to help navigate through different obstacles. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/Runner_NChAAfMzx3.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>Each of the four themed worlds adds unique mechanics to the field, giving even the most crabby player hours of entertainment with 100 levels in their claws. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/new_levelselect.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>And if thats not enough...<br><br>Perfect levels and earn currency to spin at the &quot;Gachapon-d&quot; to win over 40 unique skins!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/new_gachapon.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>Snap to the beat with the nostalgic chiptune soundtrack!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/Runner_z10jibVB9o.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>And did we mention CRAB FACTS?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2457870/extras/Runner_E4q1m2gNLB.gif?t=1697731230\" /><br><br>The game was originally created for the SD IGDA 2020 Game Jam, and won 1st place. Sandy's Great Escape was created in GameMaker.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item